Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:57.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118.554,508)}海绵宝宝\N家庭派对
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临海绵宝宝的家庭派对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to "SpongeBob's House Party"
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.54,0:00:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东道主是  海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:00:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your host, Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对里有潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There'll be punch
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.51,0:01:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干  爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cookies, explosions
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及海绵宝宝的全新剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a brand-new episode of SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加利福尼亚恩斯诺现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, live from Encino, California
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.72,0:01:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请东道主海盗派斯给大家热情拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get ready for a warm embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from our party host, Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:17.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.997,624)}派对这边请
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开我家草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off my lawn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.82,0:01:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Party?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.67,0:01:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边没开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Geez, there ain't no party here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.45,0:01:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.77,0:01:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.79,0:01:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hush, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.67,0:01:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来我在赶流氓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can't you see I'm trying to keep out the riffraff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Riffraff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是看电视的观众  缺心眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's our television audience, barnacle-breath
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.33,0:01:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just fooling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们没请海绵宝宝来参加派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you didn't bring SpongeBob with you, did you?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿他收到邀请函了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, I sure hope he got his invitation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.07,0:01:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是很想去参加派对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like to go to this party
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我看不懂邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't read the invitation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, neither
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送邀请函的那位肯定一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever sent this obviously has no idea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生活有多少物理限制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about the physical limitations of life underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是都丢火里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, might as well throw these in the fire
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给大家介绍一下来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you around
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是美人鱼米妮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's Minnie Mermaid
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,米妮跳舞跳太累  现在在纳凉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minnie's cooling off on account of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she's been dancing her scales off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊  米妮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Minnie, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是在休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a little breakie-poo?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.75,0:02:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我不待在水里就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,actually I'm in here because if I wasn't, I would die
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来找找  你还不认识谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, who else haven't you met?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是长胡子海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Longbeard, the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  长胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Longbeard
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,long time no see
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢打扰海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares to interrupt Neptune?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  神哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Neppy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位是海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,统治全海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's king of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们玩得开心不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You kids having fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,办派对可真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hosting a party is hard work, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒让我想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝办派对的那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the time when SpongeBob was hosting a party
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想看那集动画片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You kids want to see that cartoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  播动画片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then, launch the cartoon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.99,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,347)}大闹派对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.59\pos(267.721,408)}分镜总监
