Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(848.178,264)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  便宜货超市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Barg'n Mart--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消费者的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a consumer's paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放眼望去堆满了各种名牌仿品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of brand-like items stocked as far as the eye can see
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,19秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,19 seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破记录了  卢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a new record, Lou
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块四毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$1.42
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过想让它变成官方记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not an official record
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先把它记在记录册上面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we record it in the Book of Records
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1182.643,310)}记录册
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,19秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"19 seconds"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共一块四毛二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's $1.42
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请在这边签名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sign here, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Initial here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.97,0:03:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.39,0:03:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  是我第一次过来给你拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a picture I took of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the first time I ever came here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你  好年轻好快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at you, so young and happy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好的时光渐行渐远到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do the years go?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(665.925,302)}动手办派对装备
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动手办派对装备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Plan Your Own Party Kit"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卢  要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lou, how much?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是说动手办派对装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the Plan Your Own Party Kit?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在买有优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're having a special on those
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're free
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you have to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动手办派对装备上面写着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,According to the Plan Your Own Party Kit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先一定要做邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,invitations are the first order of business
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宾客名单要简短
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"A short guest list
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只请最亲近的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"consisting of only your closest acquaintances
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能为整晚奠定温馨基调
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"will set an intimate tone for the evening
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使得派对得以成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and provide soirée success"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard the man, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只请最亲近的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only our closest friends
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底谁是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who the barnacles is SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你跟他是幼儿园同学吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe you went to kindergarten with him, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(826.147,196)}珊瑚队加油
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幼儿园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kindergarten, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1172.629,772)}贝壳老师班
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来现在又得搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's time to move again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  这套动手办派对装备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, this Plan Your Own Party Kit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮上大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a real lifesaver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:54.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(247.344,830)}奶油乐
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没它我怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How else would I have known
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要做新鲜的凝脂生奶油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make freshly whipped clotted cream?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  快叫宇航员来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you better call an astronomer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我做的这凝脂奶油棒出地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because this clotted cream is out of this world
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的皮纳塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My piñata
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动手办派对装备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Plan Your Own Party Kit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我装皮纳塔的时候得发挥创意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,encourages creativity when stuffing your piñata
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以要装恶魔蛋  不装糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using deviled eggs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问得好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good question, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动手办派对装备有警告说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Plan Your Own Party Kit warns
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对不好好管理容易玩完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that unsupervised parties can lead to disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才冒昧制定了一份时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I've taken the liberty of devising a schedule--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点到八点零五
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8:00 to 8:05
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,guests arrive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点零五到八点十五
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8:05 to 8:15
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开场白与综合讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,opening remarks and general discussion;
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点十五到八点二十七
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8:15 to 8:27
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做手工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,craft corner
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并发放名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,followed by name tag distribution
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点二十七分进行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At 8:27 we begin
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃饼干兼绕口令大赛的资格赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the qualifying rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for our cracker-eating/ tongue-twister contest
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点零七  猜字谜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:07, running charades
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点三十八  慈善咬苹果游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:38, charity apple-bob
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734.019,796)}舞步
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点五十七  电子吉特巴舞马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:57, electric jitterbug dance marathon--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女生的不二之选
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ladies' choice
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十点零九  精彩一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At 10:09, things start cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时我要开始做举世闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as I dip into my world famous
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲门笑话撑杆跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knock-knock joke vault
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要照着时间表上面的做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as long as we stick to this schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对保证成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our party is a guaranteed success
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是史上最酷派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the coolest party ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.37,0:06:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前海绵宝宝的派对筹办得很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's smooth party sailing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for SpongeBob so far
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在换我来开派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for me to get me own party underway
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,围过来  坏血病旱鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gather round, you scurvy landlubbers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来学幸福假腿舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to learn the Peg-legged Dance of Happiness
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's quite simple really
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只需要一根假腿  再多加耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you need is a peg leg and some patience
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外买我的教学系列
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my instructional video series
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要二十九块九毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only $29.95
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(824.145,152)}派斯舞蹈指南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1148.595,558)}立即下单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(283.394,360)}狂舞不止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365.508,806)}只要二十九块九毛五
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太俗气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How tacky
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.05,0:06:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原价可是要四十块的  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a $40 value, Potty, a $40 value
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.47,0:06:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这舞非常好跳  非常好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, it's very easy and loads of fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐队到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, the band's here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.06,0:06:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Band?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What band?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给派对雇来的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The band I hired for the party
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错嘛  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A jolly idea, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现场音乐让派对可以更热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little live music'll get me shindig dug
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个乐队  藤壶比尔与七大洋乐队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who'd you get, Barnacle Bill and the Seven Seas?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草萨丽和她的爱笑海龟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seaweed Sally and her cackling turtle?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大副兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The First Mates
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.14,0:07:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盐水山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salt Water Sam
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特邀歌手有海水兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,featuring the Brine Brothers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生锈铰链
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rusty Hinges
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与关禁闭乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the Boys from the Brig?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几年前早散伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They broke up years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那请的是哪个乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, who else is there?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鸟头乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Bird Brains
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鸟头乐队  比其他那堆乐队都强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Bird Brains-- they're better than those other bands
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可它们就只是群鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they're just a bunch of birds
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  恩斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Encino
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:26.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639.889,722)}鸟头乐队
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  刚刚那是我听过最难听的船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Potty, that's the worst sea chantey I've every heard
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好别吵上加吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope it doesn't get any louder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop the music
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你们的音乐就只有鸟会觉得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you fellas sound real good around the birdbath
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在这是在电视直播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but this here is basic cable
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这是重要时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the big time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕你们现在得走甲板落海去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it's time for you to walk the plank
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我们被解雇了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean we're fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, start jumping
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就拿我剑刺你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you're going to be dealing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the business end of me sword
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了你们是鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot that you're birds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:44.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,814)}请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁派斯还没平复情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While Patchy pulls himself together
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看海绵宝宝的派对办得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's see how SpongeBob's party is shaping up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916.273,598)}派对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762.058,140)}开心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:51.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918.275,224)}享用美食
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  快准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary, get ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快八点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's almost 8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here they come
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在才八点零十秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's only ten seconds past 8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在八点零二十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's 20 seconds past 8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半都没收到邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe nobody got their invitations
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点零三十秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,30 seconds past 8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没一个来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's coming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最烂东道主非我莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst host ever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一位客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first guest
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才迟到了四十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and only 40 seconds late
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能不能夸你迟到得甚是光鲜亮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I compliment you on being fashionably late?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我给你打杯潘趣酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get you a glass of punch?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你路痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you have any trouble finding the place?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说潘趣酒行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So is the punch okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad, not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice weather we're having
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实很温和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been very mild, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.10,0:09:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个季节就该温和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mild season
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那  你看没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you read any?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对又来几个客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More party guests
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请让小蜗帮忙保管你的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let Gary take your coat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后由我来为你献上开胃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then allow me to offer you some hors d'oeuvres
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a glass of punch
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不介意我就开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了俩  还剩175个没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two down, 175 to go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1066.481,270)}宾客名单
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这些名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These name tags
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用不着尴尬的自我介绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eliminate the need for awkward introductions
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来几个客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More guests
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.02,0:10:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星大派是我  子女尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Kcirtap si eman ym o-77-eh"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz180\pos(746.036,722)}你好  我是派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个傻小子看错了  上面写的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you dumb bunny, it says
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  我是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hello, my name is Patrick"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点零三分才安排大家笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The laughter isn't scheduled until 9:03
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开派对就自家开去  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to throw a party, do it at your house, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.51,0:10:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是在跟你说话  还是跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was he talking to me or you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you made it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我电视坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My cable's out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我深表遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear about that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how's it going, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你跟蟹老板安排了轻松对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have you making light conversation with Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但仅限十点四十一到十点四十七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from 10:41 to 10:47
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要是你非得急着说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you've got a case of the jabber-jaws
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就能给你把聊天对象改成史酷特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can pair you up right now with Scooter
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是破冰用的话题卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are some topic cards to break the ice
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门口来客了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone's at the door
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的卡上写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine says
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先有牡蛎  还是先有珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Which came first, the oyster or the pearl?"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你支持珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You take the side of the pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太烂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is lame
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的卡上写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My card says
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探讨讽刺的哲学本质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Discuss the philosophical nature of irony"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的卡上写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does yours say?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼貌点头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nod politely
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的上面写什么  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does yours say, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  上面写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it says
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(994.381,844)}你要说\N你从哪里来
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨论蟹黄堡秘方的神秘配料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Discuss the secret ingredient
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Krabby Patty formula"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How interesting
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得美  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员  最后一位客人的抵达时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, the final guest is about to arrive
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟到22分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,22 minutes late
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936.3,708)}薯片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, please
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.83,0:12:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然都到齐了  那我正式宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that we're all here, I officially declare
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对正式启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the party switch to be in the "on" position
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.11,0:12:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我在更衣室里换完衣服回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As soon as I get back from the coatroom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就来介绍今晚安排的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll have a rundown of tonight's scheduled events
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:36.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(669.93,170)}大衣保管处
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别丢下我就开玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try not to have too much fun without me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That includes you folks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:42.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118.554,508)}海绵宝宝\N家庭派对
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的家庭派对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"SpongeBob's House Party"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广告过后马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be right back after these messages
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118.554,508)}海绵宝宝\N家庭派对
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回到  海绵宝宝的家庭派对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back to "SpongeBob's House Party"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916.273,598)}派对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:06.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(687.956,828)}小费
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我又给你找了件大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gar, got another coat for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  派对一定会特好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The party's going great, by the way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会成为大家长期长期讨论的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're going to be talking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about this one for a long, longtime
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to "work"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员  来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, let's
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我派对是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening to my party?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看时间表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you read the schedule?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上十点  狂舞不止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"10:00 pm: Dance your pants off"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上十点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10:00 pm
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着时间表上面玩  行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try to stick to the schedule, shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点五十二分才吃光蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cake will be eaten at 8:52, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点五十二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8:52
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(894.242,598)}吹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.975,762)}吸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家可不可以看过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have everyone's attention, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.90,0:14:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家往沙发上坐好  让我妥善安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If everyone could take a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the couch while I sort this out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢配合  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常感谢大家耐心等候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey everybody, thanks for your patience
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知  万事开头难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know we've gotten off to a rocky start here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要带大家重回正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm going to get us back on track
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在八点三十七了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is now 8:37
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都知道什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we all know what that means
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来念报纸漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to read aloud from the newspaper comics
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(531.739,166)}漫画
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像还
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挺刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,real thrill
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.20,0:14:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找找看  就先开始念小聪明一族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, I think I'll start out with "The Wisenheimers"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  版面一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, panel one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小聪明罗克西在使某种耙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we see Roxy Wisenheimer with some sort of rake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  这我不能念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I can't read from this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这张是昨天的报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is yesterday's paper
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿今天的报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just grab today's paper
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你可太会开派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you sure know how to throw a party
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人没我还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would they do without me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锁外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Locked out?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这首歌节拍真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This song's got a great beat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咚咚咚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"knock, knock"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么里面的都听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, I wonder why they don't hear me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面的都没用话题卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not using the topic cards
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即兴创作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ad-libbing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下派大星成众矢之的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now they're mad at Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在狂吃恶魔蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's hogging the deviled eggs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看那些可怜的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at those poor souls
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定无聊到快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're so bored they've gone mad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对都乱成一锅粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The party's falling into chaos
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全怪我东道主没能带大家回正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without my hosting talents to guide it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你常来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you come here often?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  海绵宝宝家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SquarePants residence
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140.584,360)}电话
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想找海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to talk to SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm outside
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别挂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有电话找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phone's for you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.28,0:15:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你先别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  他不在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he's not out there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你找海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, dude, if you're looking for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就去潘趣酒碗那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's over by the punchbowl
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电话给你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.04,0:16:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把电话放潘趣酒碗里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phone in punchbowl?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没列入时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not even on the schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帅哥拉里  你可真是秀色可餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry, my man, you are looking good enough to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过得涂点牙齿增白剂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could use a little teeth-whitener, though
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝肯定不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure SpongeBob won't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他梳子长得也太怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check out his crazy comb
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  好像有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, sounds like someone's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在翻我药箱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rummaging through my medicine cabinet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望那谁别碰我的特制梳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope they don't touch my special comb
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,通风得也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I've aired it out enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对终于开始精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This party's finally starting to pick up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望影响不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope this doesn't interfere
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点二十的手指玩偶剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with finger-puppet theater at 9:20
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是没法进去恢复秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't get back inside and restore order
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半就没时间办安排的活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there might not be time for any of the scheduled events
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝也太会开派对了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, SpongeBob really knows how to throw a great party
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything is quite lovely
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过他的画作品味我可不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Although I don't care for his taste in paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道怎么会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even know how that happened
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来也没得选了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I have no choice
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要挖地道进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to tunnel back in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, don't panic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东道主回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The host has returned
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop, hop
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说我还能接受不用话题卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can take losing the topic cards
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还让电话放潘趣酒里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the phone in the punchbowl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但本来应该是我要带头兔兔跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I was supposed to lead the bunny hop
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂到不能再烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a bunch of barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要闯进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm breaking in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢匪兔兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A burglar bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说作案动机是啥呢  奥马利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do they do it, O'Malley?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是以此为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's probably how he gets his kicks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这种罪犯让我想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You criminals make me sick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm no criminal
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就住这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I live here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.68,0:17:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just throwing a party
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的被锁在门外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got locked out, I swear
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,误会可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a terrible misunderstanding
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你派对愉快  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have a nice party now, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚我差点就以为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, for a second there I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会因为私闯我家被逮捕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was going to be arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for breaking into my own house
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突然来个那样的反转也太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What an ironic twist that would have been
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're throwing a party
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不邀请我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why weren't we invited?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不知道你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you'd
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动手办派对装备没说要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plan Your Own Party Kit didn't mention
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the police
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么爱说就跟法官说去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, motor-mouth, tell it to the judge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手铐坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These cuffs are broken
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手套坏了就不能押他坐牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't bring him in in broken cuffs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车上有副旧的还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an old pair in the car we can use
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在给你们打潘趣酒还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to offer you some punch?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  你有权保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have the right to remain silent
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己冷冰冰地整晚坐大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All night in a stony lonesome
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得穿着兔兔装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a bunny outfit
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, the door's locked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:51.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776.078,694)}你好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我就把备用钥匙放在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I keep a spare key under
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垫子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.27,0:18:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对已经烂完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This party was a complete disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我们大家参加过最棒的派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the greatest party any of us have ever been to
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是史上最佳派对东道主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you are the best party-thrower ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得把你的所作所为都记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you did, you should write it down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周末再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and do it again next weekend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再次谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.32,0:19:21.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:21.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've done it again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来我还是挺会办派对的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I know how to throw a party after all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你玩得可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like you had a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的派对圆满成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,old SpongeBob's party worked out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该我来办我自己的派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I got to get me own party going
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  准备好听听真正的音乐没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, are you ready for some real music, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这种人不能得坏血病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scurvy ain't for the likes of me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这种人不能得坏血病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scurvy ain't for the likes of me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该你来长笛独奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for your flute solo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不吹长笛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't play a flute
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吹的是横笛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I play a fife
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然没被炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I survived that one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  鸟头乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, The Bird Brains
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(473.658,966)}鸟头乐队
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.92,0:20:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来到我最爱的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come with me to the land I love
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地址不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not right here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不在街边和天上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down the street or up above
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.22,0:21:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在蔚蓝海洋最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's down below in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.79,0:21:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝住在这  大家一起乐逍遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where SpongeBob lives and the fun is always free
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(267.371,680)}欢乐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下下下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, down, down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜到海洋最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the bottom of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where our salty friend SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waits for you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下下下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, down, down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起乐逍遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, we'll have lots of fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.32,0:21:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你和我永远沐浴在海底阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and me forever in the underwater sun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家如果有机会  就来捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll catch some jellyfish if we get a chance
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.39,0:21:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟派大星打招呼  美美跳个舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Patrick and do a little dance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.975,450)}你好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟珊迪打空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate-chop Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看章鱼哥晒日光浴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See Squid get a tan
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.92,0:21:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃一个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阻止痞老板的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And foil Plankton's plan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(826.147,896)}邪恶诡计
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下下下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, down, down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.07,0:21:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜到海洋最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the bottom of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会合海绵宝宝  和他的蜗牛小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll hook up with SpongeBob and his snail, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.41,0:22:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下下下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, down, down
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.50,0:22:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起乐逍遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll have lots of fun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.50,0:22:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你和我永远沐浴在海底阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and me forever in the underwater sun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwater sun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.67,0:22:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great job, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.27,0:22:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for stopping by
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.20,0:22:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出门可别让舷窗给撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let the porthole hit you on the way out
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也感谢你们的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thank you for stopping by
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.80,0:22:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让这场派对乐趣加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made this party a real fun time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣妹们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ladies are here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.38,0:22:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.32,0:22:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiver me timbers
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎辣妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, girlies
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.02,0:22:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要找就找波蒂去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Potty you're after
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.97,0:22:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop with the kissing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.83,0:22:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家光临
